other_tests.findings: Mild bibasilar dependent atelectasis, multiple hypodensities in the spleen measuring to 8 mm, no free air, free fluid, or pathologic lymphadenopathy in the abdomen. There is florid sigmoidal diverticulosis with fat stranding suggesting developing phlegmon and locules of air suggesting microperforation. Marked prostatic enlargement to 9.0 x 7.4 cm.
